  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to \"Milo's Tiny Fish Pond\" – Your Personal Cyber Fish Pond!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tired of complicated controls? Craving a moment of relaxing, healing fun? This unique desktop idle fish-keeping game lets you own a vibrant underwater world, even amidst your busy schedule.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relax & Idle, Earn While You Chill:</strong> Say goodbye to grinding! Your fish grow, play, and accumulate \"Mili\" (in-game currency) for you 24/7. Even when the game is closed, offline earnings continue, bringing pleasant surprises every time you return.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/304fafc8f9d72e2bf2b8d6de22156baa.poster.avif?t=1765626024\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/304fafc8f9d72e2bf2b8d6de22156baa.webm?t=1765626024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/304fafc8f9d72e2bf2b8d6de22156baa.mp4?t=1765626024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Surprise Packs, Collectible Fun:</strong> Open various magical fish packs to discover adorable fish of different shapes and rarities. Nurture them carefully, watch them grow from fry to profitable adults, and satisfy your collector's itch!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/c5503ea02ad609e89dd6a8c1f4a89109.poster.avif?t=1765626024\" width=800 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/c5503ea02ad609e89dd6a8c1f4a89109.webm?t=1765626024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/c5503ea02ad609e89dd6a8c1f4a89109.mp4?t=1765626024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interactive Feeding, Faster Growth:</strong> Want your fish to grow faster? Simply right-click on the water surface to feed them delicious fish food. Watching them eagerly compete for food is incredibly soothing.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/36b328b076342658c39236f8784c1b58.poster.avif?t=1765626024\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/36b328b076342658c39236f8784c1b58.webm?t=1765626024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/36b328b076342658c39236f8784c1b58.mp4?t=1765626024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pond Upgrades, Infinite Possibilities:</strong> Unlock and upgrade more uniquely styled fish ponds. Not only can they accommodate more beloved fish, but they can also house different species, creating diverse underwater ecosystems.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/76d9e3e521dd1df042efd4ff59188fbb.poster.avif?t=1765626024\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/76d9e3e521dd1df042efd4ff59188fbb.webm?t=1765626024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/76d9e3e521dd1df042efd4ff59188fbb.mp4?t=1765626024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Personalized Decor, Style It Your Way:</strong> Use a dazzling array of decorations to turn your fish pond into a unique landscape. From aquatic plants to rockeries, backgrounds to ornaments, everything is defined by you. Unwanted decorations can even be sold back at their original price, making it easy to experiment with different styles!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/7579d6984b5e55e681be6d16ff69a94c.poster.avif?t=1765626024\" width=800 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/7579d6984b5e55e681be6d16ff69a94c.webm?t=1765626024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/7579d6984b5e55e681be6d16ff69a94c.mp4?t=1765626024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Desktop Companion, Real-time Charm:</strong> Let the fish pond become part of your dynamic desktop. See your fish swim gracefully whenever you glance down during work or study, adding a touch of life and ease to your digital world.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/2fad9024e681fe23634baaf9ddf65066.poster.avif?t=1765626024\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/2fad9024e681fe23634baaf9ddf65066.webm?t=1765626024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/2fad9024e681fe23634baaf9ddf65066.mp4?t=1765626024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【Gameplay Summary】</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit the shop to purchase your desired fish packs and ponds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open fish packs and place the cute fish into the corresponding ponds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feed your fish periodically to speed up their growth and increase earnings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade ponds and unlock decorations to create your personalized underwater world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your fish collection, selling surplus fish for Mili.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the continuous income and collecting fun from effortless idling!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join \"Milo's Desktop Pond\" now, start your desktop fish-keeping journey, and let these lovely little fish brighten your every day!</strong>🌿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
