img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/2fad9024e681fe23634baaf9ddf65066.poster.avif?t=1765626024\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/2fad9024e681fe23634baaf9ddf65066.webm?t=1765626024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573000/extras/2fad9024e681fe23634baaf9ddf65066.mp4?t=1765626024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【Gameplay Summary】</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit the shop to purchase your desired fish packs and ponds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open fish packs and place the cute fish into the corresponding ponds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feed your fish periodically to speed up their growth and increase earnings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade ponds and unlock decorations to create your personalized underwater world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your fish collection, selling surplus fish for Mili.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the continuous income and collecting fun from effortless idling!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join \"Milo's Desktop Pond\" now, start your desktop fish-keeping journey, and let these lovely little fish brighten your every day!</strong>🌿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
